@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram - Healthcare Portal

[*] --> Registration

state Registration <<choice>>
state "Registration Success" as RegSuccess
state "Registration Failure" as RegFailure
state Login
state LoginDecision <<choice>>
state "Invalid Login" as InvalidLogin
state "Valid Login" as ValidLogin
state FacilityAccess
state NewsContent
state HealthChecking
state ResultView
state PaymentMethodSelection
state CashPaymentDetails
state InsurancePayment
state FeedbackCollection
state Logout

Registration : entry / To Action
Registration : do / Register user
Registration : exit / Registration successful or failed

RegSuccess : entry / User registered successfully
RegSuccess : do / Proceed to login
RegSuccess : exit / Login page

RegFailure : entry / Registration failed
RegFailure : do / Show error message
RegFailure : exit / Abnormal termination

Login : entry / To Action
Login : do / Log in to the system
Login : exit / Username and password entered

InvalidLogin : entry / Trying to log in
InvalidLogin : do / Invalid username and password
InvalidLogin : exit / Back to login page

ValidLogin : entry / Student logged in
ValidLogin : do / Provide access to available facilities
ValidLogin : exit / Facility Access page

FacilityAccess : entry / User signed in
FacilityAccess : do / Show available facilities
FacilityAccess : exit / Facility Access page

NewsContent : entry / User signed in
NewsContent : do / Show news and expert content
NewsContent : exit / News Content page

HealthChecking : entry / User signed in
HealthChecking : do / Allow health-related information access
HealthChecking : exit / Health Checking page

ResultView : entry / After viewing a result
ResultView : do / Continue using the system or finish session
ResultView : exit / Result View page

PaymentMethodSelection : entry / User selected payment method
PaymentMethodSelection : do / Show cash or insurance options
PaymentMethodSelection : exit / Payment Method Selection page

CashPaymentDetails : entry / Cash payment chosen
CashPaymentDetails : do / Show cash payment details
CashPaymentDetails : exit / Cash Payment Details page

InsurancePayment : entry / Insurance payment chosen
InsurancePayment : do / Process and validate insurance
InsurancePayment : exit / Insurance Payment page

FeedbackCollection : entry / After service completion
FeedbackCollection : do / Collect user feedback
FeedbackCollection : exit / Feedback Collection page

Logout : entry / End of session
Logout : do / Log out users
Logout : exit / Abnormal termination

Registration --> Login
Login --> LoginDecision
LoginDecision --> InvalidLogin
LoginDecision --> ValidLogin
InvalidLogin --> Registration
ValidLogin --> FacilityAccess
FacilityAccess --> NewsContent
NewsContent --> HealthChecking
HealthChecking --> ResultView
ResultView --> PaymentMethodSelection
PaymentMethodSelection --> CashPaymentDetails
CashPaymentDetails --> InsurancePayment
InsurancePayment --> FeedbackCollection
FeedbackCollection --> Logout
@enduml
